item.title: About Me
item.description: The background, Thought Process, and Goals Cornell University graduate B.S. in Engineering Physics & Computer Science Minor in Public Policy Born and Raised in Wilmington, North Carolina I was born and raised in Wilmington, North Carolina. After I graduated high school, I have been attending Cornell University, enrolled in the College of Engineering as an Engineering Physics major. I have always loved math as a child and developed a love for physics and politics as I went on in high school.
